author: philip
msg: Fix a bug revealed by valgrind where pool memory was referenced
after the pool had been cleared.  Thanks to Greg Hudson for
explaining credential lifetimes.
* subversion/libsvn_subr/auth.c (svn_auth_first_credentials): Allocate
hash key from the auth baton pool.

author: philip
msg: * subversion/tests/libsvn_repos/run-repos-tests.py: Set svn:executable.

author: philip
msg: * subversion/libsvn_ra_dav/fetch.c (end_element): Avoid a compiler
warning about an unitialized variable by calling abort on an
impossible code path.

author: philip
msg: Add -c (last changed) and -n (no newline) options to svnversion. Fix
a leaked error discovered during development.
* subversion/svnversion/main.c
(struct status_baton): Add committed member.
(analyze_status): Use either current revision or last changed revision.
(usage): Add apr_getopt_option_t* paramater, tweak text, print options.
(main): Make argv const, add option and newline processing.
* subversion/include/svn_error.h
(SVN_INT_ERR): Clear error.

author: rooneg
msg: * subversion/bindings/swig/swigutil_pl.c
(perl_callback_thunk): make the format string argument const, which fixes
a few warnings about passing const strings to this function.
